I saw you in his car.

31
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,160
I also saw the two of you...

32
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,520
This is my private matter.

33
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,530
It's none of your business.

34
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,640
How can you say
it's none of my business?

35
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,920
What about what happened between us?

36
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,440
Wasn't that a major life event?

37
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:23,990
What happened between us?

38
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:33,120
Do I have to take responsibility for you
for life?

39
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,200
Naive.

40
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,120
Immature.

41
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,200
Go back and get some sleep.

42
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,080
Li Guangnan,

43
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,280
am I naive?

44
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,800
Both foolish and naive.

45
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,040
Oh, Lu Xiaolu.

46
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:26,160
You've encountered an expert.

47
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,880
What do you mean?

48
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,520
Do you know there's a type of woman

49
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,880
