59
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,080
Well, it seems like you don't know.

60
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,800
Bai Lan was transferred to
the Second Light Industry Bureau

61
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,800
to work as Bi Zhigang's father's translator.

62
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,440
I'm not making this up.

63
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,360
My mom told me.

64
00:04:04,370 --> 00:04:05,950
It's been spreading
around the women's dormitory,

65
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,180
and you're the only one who doesn't know.

66
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,760
Well, that's good in a way.

67
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,520
