in the boiler room.

68
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:18,680
Suffer?

69
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:21,080
Bi Zhigang can make Bai Lan suffer?

70
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,320
Bi Zhigang

71
