What I mean to say is,

76
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,960
if you compare yourself to Bi Zhigang,

77
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,400
he has a background, education,

78
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,360
and a good father.

79
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,600
What do you have?

80
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,240
I...

81
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,520
You do have one advantage.

82
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,520
