at the food factory.

156
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,600
I volunteered.

157
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,280
The Bureau selected based on merit.

158
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,360
What does it have to do with you?

159
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:10,920
I heard that

160
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,440
the Bureau has a fully funded slot

161
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,880
to study for a master's
in Shanghai this year.

162
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,760
There's only one slot,

163
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,200
and many people are

164
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,040
competing for it.

165
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,720
My dad said

166
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,840
they must choose the most capable person

167
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:27,050
to make everyone trust the result.

168
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,440
Of course,

169
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:29,360
you don't need to worry.

170
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,160
I'll do everything I can

171
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,320
to help you.

172
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,320
But it also depends on
your own capabilities.

173
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,040
I don't think I need your help.

174
