182
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,760
Come over here.

183
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,640
Help me watch the stove.

184
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,080
Aren't you free right now?

185
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,600
The soup is for the whole family,

186
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,840
but I'm the only one cooking.

187
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,420
Can't I take a break
and read the newspaper?

188
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,400
Right?

189
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,480
What are you cooking?

190
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,740
My dad asked me to...

191
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,920
Why are you so insistent on cooking?

192
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,000
He insisted on doing it.

193
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,680
This is my job, you know.

194
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,800
Come on, give it to me.

195
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,320
Okay, good boy.

196
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,200
Hey, come back.

197
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:46,760
Alright,

198
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:47,640
