199
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:54,870
Dad,

200
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:58,760
have you heard of that strange syndrome?

201
00:09:59,040 --> 00:09:59,880
What syndrome?

202
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,680
It is called Stockholm Syndrome.

203
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,600
I know.

204
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:06,840
The victim falls in love
with the perpetrator, right?

205
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,520
Don't you think you have this syndrome?

206
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,760
Alright, son.

207
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,240
You've grown up.

208
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,040
You know how to use sarcasm now.

209
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:18,760
Dad,

210
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:20,040
that's not what I meant.

211
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,360
But the truth is

212
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:22,880
since I was little,

213
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,990
you did whatever Mom asked.

214
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,690
