215
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,920
Are you really so afraid of Mom?

216
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,120
Afraid?

217
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:31,520
You don't understand.

218
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,600
Let me tell you,

219
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,360
there's no man in this world

220
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,400
who's afraid of his wife.

221
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,240
This is about respect.

222
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:40,720
It's about love, tolerance

223
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,760
and trust.

224
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,560
Do you understand?

225
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,760
Well, let me ask you another question.

226
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:48,720
Go ahead.

227
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:51,480
If Mom gets close to

228
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,830
someone you really dislike

229
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,160
and does things you don't understand,

230
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,560
what would you do?

231
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,440
You should ask her.

232
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,280
Why are you asking me?

233
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,920
