236
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,280
How did you ask her?

237
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,960
Did you ask calmly

238
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,200
or assertively?

239
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,120
How can you stay calm

240
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,560
when something like that happens?

241
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:16,880
This matter

242
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,760
is very simple. It...

243
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,440
