an interesting conversation.

244
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,760
What are you talking about?

245
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,800
Nothing.

246
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,680
About relationship issues?

247
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:28,320
No.

248
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:30,160
