about relationship issues?

249
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,800
Your dad is like a fool in that aspect.

250
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,800
What does he know?

251
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,280
You should ask me about that.

252
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,400
I'm right here.

253
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,720
Let me tell you

254
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,160
