255
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,320
Love is all about trust.

256
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,560
What did you just say?

257
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,280
You questioned her?

258
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,280
How could you question her?

259
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,320
If you lose trust,

260
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,200
love will run away,

261
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,440
right?

262
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,560
Tell me.

263
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,080
Are you dating someone?

264
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,680
No.

265
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:04,600
Tell me what happened.

266
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,200
Which girl is it?

267
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:09,040
- Mom.
- Well...

268
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:11,240
Stop asking if he doesn't want to say.

269
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,760
Remember, it's only about

270
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,800
trust.

271
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,200
Look at me.

272
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,720
I trust your mom completely,

273
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:18,120
right?

274
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,320
Of course.

275
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,360
Trust.

276
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,080
You understand?

277
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,800
Mom, Dad just lied to you earlier.

278
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:26,280
He asked me to watch the stove.

279
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,480
Hey, you brat, how can you...

280
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,240
I have always done this alone.

281
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,480
That brat.

282
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,520
So stingy.

283
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,280
Hey, hey, why is she here?

284
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,720
She's a big shot at the SLI Bureau now.

285
