00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:46,240
People, like cars,
come in different varieties,

454
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:48,880
but it's not about money;

455
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,800
it's about whether your heart is clean.

456
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,960
Don't think you're special just because

457
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,330
your dad is a director.

