00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:44,680
This matter is not over!

491
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:45,920
Not over!

492
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,520
Hey, Xiaolu is here.

493
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:58,080
Xiaolu, we've heard about it.

494
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,160
