569
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,840
Let me tell you, this fight can't happen.

570
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:41,420
If it does, it'll affect your skating rink.

571
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:43,480
You don't understand?

572
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:44,720
Secretary Hong has always been

573
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:46,040
dissatisfied with your use

574
00:23:46,080 --> 00:23:47,920
of factory land for the skating rink.

575
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:49,720
Now that he's the factory director,

576
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:52,160
if his higher-up's son gets beaten up...

577
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:53,440
Think about it.

578
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,800
Do you still want the skating rink?

579
00:23:57,800 --> 00:23:58,640
Alright,

580
00:23:59,120 --> 00:23:59,960
Ding,

581
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,000
I'll handle this.

582
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,720
Don't take it lightly.

583
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:04,600
Talk to him nicely.

584
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:06,080
- I have to go.
- Okay.

585
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,320
Easy.

586
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,080
Each of us

587
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:20,000
- will wield a stick like this.
- Let me see.

588
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:21,240
Bi and his friends

589
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:22,560
will be in serious trouble.

590
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:25,720
No sticks.

591
00:24:26,600 --> 00:24:27,550
My cousin said we should not

592
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:28,720
go all out in a fight.

593
00:24:29,080 --> 00:24:29,920
It's a hidden rule.

594
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,240
We're all from the same factory.

595
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:32,560
What if someone gets seriously hurt?

596
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,800
Blind weapons can cause accidents.

597
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:34,680
But just now...

598
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:35,840
I think you're right.

599
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:37,320
Me too.

600
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:39,320
I think

601
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,200
we can do that this weekend.

602
00:24:41,220 --> 00:24:42,760
We should settle this
sooner rather than later

603
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:44,040
to prevent further complications.

604
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:45,160
Sure, whatever.

605
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:47,200
You seem to understand brawling
pretty well.

606
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:48,280
- Bro.
- Dajiang.

607
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:49,600
Why are you here?

608
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:51,560
I have so many good qualities,

609
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,840
why only learn

610
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:54,480
how to fight like me?

611
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,040
It's not like that.

612
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,400
For the sake of a woman,

613
00:24:58,280 --> 00:24:59,680
you're arranging fights now,

614
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,400
causing a huge commotion.

615
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,160
You've really grown up.

616
00:25:03,800 --> 00:25:05,120
- Dajiang...
- Dajiang,

617
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:06,640
it's not about a woman.

618
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:08,280
Bi Zhigang has gone too far.

619
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:09,440
He looks down on us workers,

620
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,120
and we can't stand for it.

621
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:12,280
It's true!

622
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:13,960
- He's right.
- It's true!

623
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:16,080
That's why

624
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,320
I've brought my brothers here.

625
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:23,120
Let's see who dares to touch my cousin.

626
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:24,440
Let's go!

627
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:25,680
- Thank you, Dajiang!
- Thanks!

628
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:27,360
- Let's go.
- Dajiang is great!

629
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,640
Xiaolu.

630
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:38,960
Why are you here?

631
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:41,360
Director Bi asked me
to check if the car was fixed.

632
00:25:41,360 --> 00:25:42,400
The foreign guests are waiting.

633
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:43,460
There was just a minor issue

634
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:44,460
with the battery connection,

635
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,360
but it's fixed now.

636
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:48,400
I'm asking you,

637
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,400
did you arrange to fight with Bi Zhigang?

638
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,960
Even you know about it?

639
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:55,480
But strictly speaking, this isn't just a fight.

640
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,240
It's a battle for justice.

641
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:58,640
That's still a fight.

642
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,280
Anyway, no matter what,

643
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,480
you must come

644
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:02,520
and see

645
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:04,280
how I knock Bi Zhigang down.

646
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:05,800
I won't come.

647
00:26:06,210 --> 00:26:07,050
Why?

648
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:08,600
Anyway, I'm telling you,

649
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,120
if you fight,

650
00:26:11,080 --> 00:26:12,080
I won't talk to you anymore.

651
00:26:21,120 --> 00:26:23,120
Hey, have you ever learned to drive?

652
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:25,560
That way!

653
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,800
Why can't you
solve problems with your brain?

654
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,120
Resorting to violence

655
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:32,240
is something barbarians do.

656
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:33,360
Whatever you say.

657
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:34,480
Just consider me a barbarian.

658
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,160
I can't back out at this point.

659
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:37,600
- You must fight?
- Yes.

660
00:26:43,280 --> 00:26:44,120
Foolish!

661
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:46,000
Selfish!

662
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:47,640
Vain!

663
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:49,960
You narcissistic men,

664
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,160
am I some kind of object?

665
00:26:52,520 --> 00:26:53,960
Whoever wins gets me as a prize?

666
00:26:54,060 --> 00:26:55,280
Your competition with Bi Zhigang

667
00:26:55,320 --> 00:26:56,720
is utterly absurd from start to finish.

668
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,200
It's not like that, Bai Lan.

669
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:02,800
I don't mean that.

670
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:08,000
Bi Zhigang is really up to no good.

671
00:27:08,170 --> 00:27:11,000
Not only does he look down on us workers,
but he deliberately placed you in the SLI Bureau

672
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,000
just to take advantage of you.

673
00:27:12,120 --> 00:27:13,950
I voluntarily went
to the Second Light Industry Bureau.

674
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:15,360
I like English, I like translation.

675
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:17,200
I don't like the boiler room.
What business is it of yours?

676
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,560
Get off!

677
00:27:20,040 --> 00:27:20,880
Get off!

678
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,920
When I sent it for repair,

679
00:27:55,080 --> 00:27:56,600
it just had a minor issue with starting.

680
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:58,080
How did it end up like this

681
00:27:58,080 --> 00:27:59,200
when it came back?

682
00:28:00,600 --> 00:28:01,950
This is the car for hosting foreign guests.

683
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:03,040
It's very delicate.

684
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:05,360
Director, I'm sorry.

685
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:07,400
It was my carelessness.

686
00:28:07,840 --> 00:28:09,200
Please give me some more time.

687
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,440
I'll find a way to fix this.

688
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:11,760
Bai Lan,

689
00:28:12,520 --> 00:28:14,280
normally you seem

690
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:15,880
quiet and composed.

691
00:28:16,120 --> 00:28:17,960
I always feel you are reliable.

692
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:19,120
Listen,

693
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,160
you can't be the type of girl

694
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,600
who treats everything lightly

695
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,760
and does things recklessly.

696
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,520
- I...
- Listen,

697
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:27,880
I'll put the issue of the training quota

698
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:29,440
on hold for now.

699
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:31,760
I think you need to go back to the factory

700
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:33,120
and gain some experience.

701
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:35,850
I want to see how you perform.

702
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:43,480
(Sunday morning at 8:00, Shipyard)

703
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:46,360
(Sunday morning at 8:00, Shipyard
Get a stretcher ready)

704
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:49,760
(Sunday morning at 8:00, Shipyard)

705
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,510
(Sunday morning at 8:00, Shipyard
Get a stretcher ready)

706
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,160
Get a stretcher ready.

707
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:12,600
♪Life fools me♪

708
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:15,480
♪Deceives me♪

709
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,760
♪Troubles me♪

710
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:19,480
Enough, Big Feet, stop singing

711
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,440
and start training seriously.

712
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:22,560
We are going to fight,

713
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:23,520
not sing.

714
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,840
Xiaolu,

715
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:26,160
I'm not going to train.

716
00:29:26,320 --> 00:29:27,160
It's too late anyway.

717
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,240
Maybe I can cheer you guys.

718
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:29,120
I'm not going.

719
00:29:30,590 --> 00:29:31,360
If you dare to back down,

720
00:29:31,380 --> 00:29:33,270
- I'll hit you right now. Do you understand?
- What are you doing?

721
00:29:33,290 --> 00:29:33,760
Stop, come here.

722
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,360
- What are you doing?
- Why are you here?

723
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:37,880
Xiaolu, you can't fight this battle.

724
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:38,720
You can't win.

725
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:41,280
Who sent you as a mediator?

726
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,200
Even if you fight, you won't win.

727
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:44,520
What do you mean?

728
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:45,960
The battle hasn't even started yet.

729
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:47,000
How can you

730
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:48,080
deflate our morale?

731
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,720
When I was
delivering files in the office,

732
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:50,600
I overheard Bi Zhigang

733
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:52,080
making a phone call to the police.

734
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:54,680
- The police?
- Yes.

735
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:55,560
I eavesdropped on him.

736
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:57,040
He told the police that the workers

737
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:58,510
were going to bring weapons
to start a fight.

738
00:29:58,540 --> 00:30:00,280
He wanted the police to arrest all of you.

739
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:02,080
How can that jerk play dirty like this?

740
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:04,800
The more he does this,

741
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,680
the less we can back down.

742
00:30:09,120 --> 00:30:10,800
Do you all want to get caught?

743
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:12,240
It's okay.

744
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,640
Let's change the location later

745
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,550
and have our brothers
keep an eye on Bi's people.

746
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:17,240
We won't let them leak information.

747
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:18,640
Yes, our factory people

748
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,880
can help us keep an eye on Bi's people.

749
00:30:20,080 --> 00:30:21,280
Are you guys crazy?

750
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:23,480
Don't worry, Little Pouter.

751
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,800
The fight between men

752
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,740
is about facing challenges
and never backing down.

753
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,040
Well said.

754
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,560
Then did you know the SLI Bureau
fired Bai Lan?

755
00:30:35,760 --> 00:30:37,480
She's starting to work
in the boiler room today.

756
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:40,080
- Really?
- I saw the notice

757
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:41,560
in the office with my own eyes.

758
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:42,960
And have you considered

759
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,000
why she was demoted?

760
00:30:44,320 --> 00:30:45,320
Everyone in the factory knows

761
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,320
who you are fighting for.

762
00:30:46,320 --> 00:30:47,620
Do you think the leadership doesn't know?

763
00:30:47,620 --> 00:30:48,840
You still have time to call it off now.

764
00:30:48,840 --> 00:30:51,560
If you really fight and cause some result,
Bai Lan won't escape unscathed.

765
00:30:59,120 --> 00:30:59,960
Enough. Stop it.

766
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:03,920
Oh, stop.

767
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,760
This is not your first time here.

768
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:13,680
You don't need me
to teach you again, right?

769
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:14,720
You need more practice.

770
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:16,040
She's pretty good at it already.

771
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:19,120
Quickly.

772
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:21,040
- Let's take a break.
- Take a break.

773
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,660
Have you heard this old saying?

774
00:31:34,840 --> 00:31:35,880
It's said that the higher

775
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,480
a person climbs,

776
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:40,000
the harder they may fall.

777
00:31:41,720 --> 00:31:43,000
Oh, Doctor Bai,

778
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:44,520
you must understand
this principle too, right?

779
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,560
It's not easy at the top, right?

780
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,240
Practice more.

781
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,280
Tired already?

782
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,200
Hurry up
or you can't finish it even tomorrow.

783
00:31:58,400 --> 00:31:59,920
Hurry up. Come on.

784
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:02,240
What are you waiting for?

785
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:05,240
Staring at me won't help you.

786
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:07,720
Move!

787
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,020
The battle is happening on Sunday.

788
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:21,360
Are you so excited that you can't sleep?

789
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:23,720
I feel the same way.

790
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:24,800
Should I

791
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:26,200
play the guitar for you

792
00:32:27,120 --> 00:32:27,960
to calm you down?

793
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:33,320
♪Should I give up, admit defeat?♪

794
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:34,160
Stop!

795
00:32:35,640 --> 00:32:36,680
The battle between experts

796
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:37,760
are more about mental state.

797
00:32:37,760 --> 00:32:38,960
Don't disturb Xiaolu.

798
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:40,680
Got it.

799
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:42,400
♪Should♪

800
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,240
Stop!

801
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:45,280
♪Should I♪

802
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:46,120
Stop!

803
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:47,800
I'll stop singing.

804
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:57,080
Ding Dezhong! I'm telling you!

805
00:32:57,280 --> 00:32:59,160
I will definitely leave the boiler room!

806
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:00,920
You narcissistic men,

807
00:33:01,320 --> 00:33:02,680
am I some kind of object?

808
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:05,000
Whoever wins gets me as a prize?

809
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:07,760
I like English, I like translation.

810
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:09,240
I voluntarily went to the SLI Bureau.

811
00:33:09,250 --> 00:33:10,200
What business is it of yours?

812
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:51,680
Dajiang,

813
00:33:52,080 --> 00:33:53,200
no matter what happens today,

814
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,360
don't start fighting

815
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:56,560
without my permission.

816
00:33:58,760 --> 00:33:59,600
Promise me.

817
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:02,400
Did you hear the news?

818
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:04,920
Lu Xiaolu is having a showdown

819
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:06,480
with Bi Zhigang this morning.

820
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:08,080
Is it true?

821
00:34:08,680 --> 00:34:09,520
Who do you think will win?

822
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:11,600
It's definitely Lu Xiaolu.

823
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,720
Bi Zhigang is so frail

824
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:14,820
that I could push him over easily.

825
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:16,440
Well, you never know.

826
00:34:16,640 --> 00:34:17,960
He's also a man.

827
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:19,200
You can't say that.

828
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,840
Although Bi Zhigang is...

829
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,080
The fight is about to start!

830
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:23,120
Let's go watch.

831
00:34:23,160 --> 00:34:24,060
- Let's go.
- Come on.

832
00:34:24,340 --> 00:34:25,320
Who are you betting on to win?

833
00:34:40,160 --> 00:34:41,240
This whole thing today

834
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,320
started because of my

835
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,600
personal grievances with Bi Zhigang.

836
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,440
To avoid dragging down others,

837
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:48,240
I propose settling it

838
00:34:48,680 --> 00:34:49,760
with a one-on-one.

839
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:51,800
- One-on-one?
- Xiaolu.

840
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,300
- You don't have to do this.
- Xiaolu.

841
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,280
You don't have to say that.

842
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:55,300
We're not afraid of him! Hit him!

843
00:34:56,720 --> 00:34:57,560
Quiet!

844
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,840
No need for a one-on-one.

845
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:01,280
Today's fight

846
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:03,320
is between Lu Xiaolu and Bi Zhigang.

